Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:56.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}深深地垂下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:01:00.92,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}抑制住急躁思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.96,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}十指缠绕牵起手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.09,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}统一步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:13.22,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}轻轻跳起  飘然回旋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:16.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}搂住腰身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:22.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}直至双唇交融之日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}歌唱起舞  进入梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}与你一同  反复演绎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}脸颊贴近胸口那时
